 begin="3:18.119" end="3:18.401">せ</span><span begin="3:18.401" end="3:18.600">る</span><span begin="3:18.600" end="3:19.048">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就能越来越珍爱自己哟</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">motto motto zibun wo ai seru yo</span></p><p begin="3:18.788" end="3:23.059" itunes:key="L58" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:18.788" end="3:19.505">鏡</span><span begin="3:19.505" end="3:19.816">を</span><span begin="3:19.816" end="3:19.945">見</span><span begin="3:19.945" end="3:20.269">て</span><span begin="3:20.269" end="3:20.388">ご</span><span begin="3:20.388" end="3:20.842">覧</span><span begin="3:20.842" end="3:21.292">よ</span><span begin="3:21.292" end="3:21.528">も</span><span begin="3:21.528" end="3:21.682">う</span><span begin="3:21.682" end="3:22.023">分</span><span begin="3:22.023" end="3:22.165">か</span><span begin="3:22.165" end="3:22.378">る</span><span begin="3:22.378" end="3:22.523">で</span><span begin="3:22.523" end="3:22.769">し</span><span begin="3:22.769" end="3:23.059">ょ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你看看镜子里 这下知道了吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">kagami wo mi te go ran yo mou wa karu desyo</span></p><p begin="3:23.059" end="3:25.746" itunes:key="L59" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:23.059" end="3:23.346">み</span><span begin="3:23.346" end="3:23.504">ん</span><span begin="3:23.504" end="3:23.724">な</span><span begin="3:23.724" end="3:23.941">を</span><span begin="3:23.941" end="3:24.179">照</span><span begin="3:24.179" end="3:24.348">ら</span><span begin="3:24.348" end="3:24.595">す</span><span begin="3:24.595" end="3:25.231">光</span><span begin="3:25.231" end="3:25.746">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那里有普照众生的光芒</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">minna wo te rasu hikari sa</span></p><p begin="3:25.862" end="3:26.595" itunes:key="L60" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:25.862" end="3:26.120">そ</span><span begin="3:26.120" end="3:26.333">う</span><span begin="3:26.333" end="3:26.595">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sousa</span></p><p begin="3:26.595" end="3:28.386" itunes:key="L61" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:26.595" end="3:27.036">神</span><span begin="3:27.036" end="3:27.319">の</span><span begin="3:27.319" end="3:27.508">ま</span><span begin="3:27.508" end="3:27.738">に</span><span begin="3:27.738" end="3:27.961">ま</span><span begin="3:27.961" end="3:28.386">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">随神之侧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">kami no manimani</span></p><p begin="3:28.386" end="3:30.142" itunes:key="L62" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:28.386" end="3:28.651">み</span><span begin="3:28.651" end="3:28.842">ん</span><span begin="3:28.842" end="3:29.081">な</span><span begin="3:29.081" end="3:29.290">あ</span><span begin="3:29.290" end="3:29.518">り</span><span begin="3:29.518" end="3:29.716">が</span><span begin="3:29.716" end="3:29.941">と</span><span begin="3:29.941" end="3:30.142">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谢谢大家</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">minna arigatou</span></p><p begin="3:30.142" end="3:33.264" itunes:key="L63" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.142" end="3:30.445">や</span><span begin="3:30.445" end="3:30.569">っ</span><span begin="3:30.569" end="3:30.830">ぱ</span><span begin="3:30.830" end="3:31.051">り</span><span begin="3:31.051" end="3:31.286">地</span><span begin="3:31.286" end="3:31.723">球</span><span begin="3:31.723" end="3:31.944">を</span><span begin="3:31.944" end="3:32.333">愛</span><span begin="3:32.333" end="3:32.612">し</span><span begin="3:32.612" end="3:32.861">て</span><span begin="3:32.861" end="3:33.264">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">果然我还是爱着地球的</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">yappari tikyuu wo ai si teru</span></p><p begin="3:33.721" end="3:35.454" itunes:key="L64" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:33.721" end="3:34.154">花</span><span begin="3:34.154" end="3:34.423">を</span><span begin="3:34.423" end="3:34.625">咲</span><span begin="3: